japanese: よぉ、将馬！/見ただろ？/俺様の雄姿！
english: Hey, Shoma! /You saw it, right? /My heroic figure!

japanese: よぉ！　夏じゃないか。/沖田先生と、なに話してたんだ？
english: Hey! Isn't that Natsu. /What were you talking about with Okita-sensei?

japanese: よし、それならいいかな。/一緒に回ろうか。
english: Alright, that's fine. /Want to go around together?

japanese: よぉ、!0！/どうだ？/学園祭は楽しんでるかァ！？
english: Hey, !0! /How is it? /Enjoying the festival!?

japanese: よぉ、もも！/部室で出し物の準備かい？
english: Hey, Momo! /Preparing the event in the club room?

japanese: よぉ、!0！/待ちに待った学園祭だぜ！/全力で楽しんでるか！？
english: Hey, !0! /The long-awaited festival! /Enjoying it fully!?

japanese: よぉ、もも！/屋上で何してるんだ？
english: Hey, Momo! /What are you doing on the roof?

japanese: よせよ、礼なんて。
english: Stop, no need to thank me.

japanese: よぉ、ザキ！/何見てるんだ？
english: Hey, Zaki! /What are you looking at?

japanese: よぉ委員長！/どうしたんだ？/そんなに血相かえて。
english: Hey Chairperson! /What's wrong? /You look so panicked.

japanese: よし、完成だ！！/二人でやるとあっという間だったな！
english: Alright, done!! /With two people it was quick!

japanese: よしよし。/では、これからもがんばりたまえ！/以上！
english: There there. /Keep working hard! /That's all!

japanese: わ、私を恋人にすると/いいじゃないですか……？/だったら、探す必要もないし……。
english: W-wouldn't making me your girlfriend be fine...? /Then no need to search...

japanese: よぉ、カノジョ！/ひとり？/ヒマなら、俺と模擬店をハシゴしないか？
english: Hey, girlfriend! /Alone? /If free, wanna hit shops with me?

japanese: よぉ、ラン。/プールで何してるんだ？
english: Hey, Ran. /What are you doing at the pool?

japanese: よしてよ、お礼なんて。
english: Stop, no need to thank me.

japanese: よぉ、もも！/どこ行くんだ？
english: Hey, Momo! /Where are you going?

japanese: よぉ、もも！/何だよ、大きなゴミ袋なんかかかえて。/ゴミ捨て係か？
english: Hey, Momo! /What's with that big trash bag? /Trash duty?

japanese: よぉ、委員長！/なかなか忙しそうだな。
english: Hey, Chairperson! /You look pretty busy.

japanese: よお、九郎！/何ひとりでブツブツいってんだ？
english: Hey, Kuro! /What are you muttering about?

japanese: よく言った！/おいオマエら！！/新しいお客のおでましだ！！
english: Well said! /Hey you guys!! /A new customer!

japanese: よしよし！/予想以上にうまくいったな！
english: There there! /Went better than expected!

japanese: よぉ、!0！/せっかくの学園祭なんだ、/一緒に見て回らないか？
english: Hey, !0! /It's the festival, /wanna look around together?

japanese: よぉ、もも！/何ひとりでブツブツいってるんだ？
english: Hey, Momo! /What are you muttering about?

japanese: よぉ、九郎じゃないか。/何やってるんだ？
english: Hey, isn't that Kuro. /What are you doing?

japanese: よぉ、委員長じゃないか。/ちょうどよかった。/これから俺と……
english: Hey, isn't that Chairperson. /Perfect timing. /Now with me...

japanese: よぉし、気合いを入れて練習だ！/……っていいたいとこだけど、/今日は、たこ焼を売らないとな。
english: Alright, practice with spirit! /...I'd like to say, but /I need to sell takoyaki today.

japanese: よぉっ、!0！/待ってたぜ！
english: Hey, !0! /I was waiting!

japanese: よぉ、!0。/キミ、悩みはないかい？
english: Hey, !0. /Any worries?

japanese: よぉ、ロイ。/何か探してるのか？
english: Hey, Roy. /Looking for something?

japanese: よぉ……ちゃんと届けといたよ。
english: Hey... I delivered it properly.

japanese: よぉ、ひなた。/今日もクラブの助っ人なのか？
english: Hey, Hinata. /Helping the club again?

japanese: よぉ、ロイ。/暇そうだな。
english: Hey, Roy. /You look bored.

japanese: よぉ、ロイ！/ヒマそうだな。
english: Hey, Roy! /You look bored.

japanese: よぉ！　!0！/フリーマーケットで売るアイテムを/募集してんだ。
english: Hey! !0! /I'm collecting items /to sell at the flea market.

japanese: わぁ、英雄先生、/これすごくいい感じですねぇ。
english: Wow, Shimazu-sensei, /this looks really good.
